---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Astro Care"
  description="How Astro Care Group Pty Ltd collects, uses and protects your personal information."
>
  <section class="mx-auto w-[min(820px,100%-2.5rem)] py-14 md:py-20">
    <p class="mb-2 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest" style="color: var(--euca);">Privacy</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-[0.95rem]" style="color: var(--tx-soft);">
      Astro Care Group Pty Ltd (ABN 99 700 192 981) · Last updated 13 July 2026
    </p>

    <div class="prose-astro mt-8 grid gap-6 text-[0.98rem] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        We collect as little personal information as we can, and we treat what you do share with us
        the way we treat the people we care for — respectfully. This policy explains what we collect,
        why, and your rights under the Privacy Act 1988 (Cth) and the Australian Privacy Principles.
      </p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl">What we collect</h2>
        <ul class="ml-5 grid list-disc gap-1.5">
          <li><strong>Callback form:</strong> your name, phone number and what you'd like help with — only when you choose to send them.</li>
          <li><strong>Chat helper:</strong> the messages you type, so the helper can answer. Don't include health details or personal identifiers in chat — for anything personal, use the callback form or phone.</li>
          <li><strong>Phone &amp; email:</strong> whatever you choose to tell us when you contact us.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">We don't use advertising trackers and the site doesn't require accounts or logins.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl">How we use it</h2>
        <ul class="ml-5 grid list-disc gap-1.5">
          <li>To call or write back when you've asked us to.</li>
          <li>To answer your questions and plan the care you've asked about.</li>
          <li>We never sell your information, and we never use it for marketing you haven't asked for.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl">Who handles it on our behalf</h2>
        <ul class="ml-5 grid list-disc gap-1.5">
          <li><strong>Form delivery:</strong> callback requests are delivered to our inbox by FormSubmit (formsubmit.co).</li>
          <li><strong>Chat:</strong> chat messages are processed by Cloudflare (hosting) and Anthropic (the AI that writes replies). Chat conversations are not used to identify you.</li>
          <li><strong>Website hosting:</strong> GitHub Pages serves this website; embedded videos are served by YouTube (privacy-enhanced mode) and play only if you press play.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl">Storage and retention</h2>
        <p>
          Enquiry details live in our email system and are kept only as long as needed to help you,
          or as the law requires. If you become a client, your care records are handled under the
          Aged Care Act and Quality Standards record-keeping rules.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl">Your rights</h2>
        <p>
          You can ask us at any time to see the personal information we hold about you, correct it,
          or delete it. Email
          <a class="font-bold underline underline-offset-4" style="color: var(--blue);" href="mailto:info@astrocare.com.au">info@astrocare.com.au</a>
          or call 1800 ASTRO (1800 278 762). If you're not happy with our response, you can complain to the
          <a class="font-bold underline underline-offset-4" style="color: var(--blue);" href="https://www.oaic.gov.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Office of the Australian Information Commissioner</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="rounded-2xl border p-4 text-[0.9rem]" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--bg-sand); color: var(--tx-soft);">
        Questions about this policy? We're happy to explain any of it in plain English —
        <a class="font-bold underline underline-offset-4" style="color: var(--blue);" href="/#contact">ask us to call you</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
